---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Used Prime Mover 2026: Finance Trucks Up to 10 Years Old with 0% Down',
  slug: 'used-prime-mover-2026-up-to-10-years',
  excerpt: 'Finance used prime movers up to 10 years old with 0% down payment. Banks reject trucks older than 5 years. Ing Heng finances based on condition.',
  date: '2026-01-08',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 6,
  category: 'Transport Vehicles',
  image: '/images/blog/prime-mover-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['used prime mover', 'old truck financing', '0% down payment', 'prime mover age limit', 'bank rejected truck'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Transport Vehicles</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Used Prime Movers: Smart Investment</h2>

      <p>Banks reject prime movers older than 5 years. But 7-10 year old trucks cost 50-60% less than new. Same earning capacity. 70-80% engine life remaining. Ing Heng Credit finances based on condition, not age.</p>

      <h2>Used Prime Mover Prices by Age</h2>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Age</th>
            <th>Price Range</th>
            <th>Engine Life Remaining</th>
            <th>Bank Policy</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>5-7 years</td>
            <td>RM140,000-RM180,000</td>
            <td>70-80%</td>
            <td>May finance (strict)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>7-10 years</td>
            <td>RM100,000-RM140,000</td>
            <td>60-70%</td>
            <td>Rejected</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>10+ years</td>
            <td>RM60,000-RM100,000</td>
            <td>50-60%</td>
            <td>Rejected</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Why Used Prime Movers Make Sense</h2>

      <h3>1. Lower Investment</h3>

      <p><strong>New Prime Mover:</strong> RM380,000</p>

      <p><strong>Used (8 years):</strong> RM120,000</p>

      <p><strong>Savings:</strong> RM260,000 (68% cheaper)</p>

      <h3>2. Same Revenue</h3>

      <p>Used prime mover generates same revenue as new:
  <br>• Normal month: RM80,000-RM100,000
  <br>• CNY month: RM120,000-RM150,000</p>

      <h3>3. Faster ROI</h3>

      <p><strong>New Truck Payback:</strong> 16-20 months</p>

      <p><strong>Used Truck Payback:</strong> 4-8 months</p>

      <h2>Bank vs. Ing Heng: Used Prime Mover</h2>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Factor</th>
            <th>Bank</th>
            <th>Ing Heng</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Age Limit</td>
            <td>5 years max</td>
            <td>No limit</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Down Payment (RM120k)</td>
            <td>RM12,000-RM24,000</td>
            <td>RM0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Approval Time</td>
            <td>2-4 weeks</td>
            <td>24-48 hours</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Inspection</td>
            <td>Reject if old</td>
            <td>Assess condition</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Financing Examples</h2>

      <h3>8-Year-Old Isuzu Giga (RM120,000)</h3>

      <p><strong>Bank:</strong> Rejected (too old)</p>

      <p><strong>Ing Heng:</strong>
  <br>• Down payment: RM0
  <br>• Loan: RM120,000 (100%)
  <br>• Monthly: ~RM2,200-RM2,600
  <br>• Term: 5-7 years</p>

      <h3>10-Year-Old Hino 500 (RM90,000)</h3>

      <p><strong>Bank:</strong> Rejected</p>

      <p><strong>Ing Heng:</strong>
  <br>• Down payment: RM0
  <br>• Loan: RM90,000 (100%)
  <br>• Monthly: ~RM1,600-RM2,000
  <br>• Term: 5-7 years</p>

      <h2>What We Look For</h2>

      <h3>Inspection Criteria</h3>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Engine Condition:</strong> Compression test, oil pressure, smoke levels</li>
        <li><strong>Transmission:</strong> Gear shifting smoothness, clutch condition</li>
        <li><strong>Chassis:</strong> Rust, structural integrity, accident damage</li>
        <li><strong>Service History:</strong> Regular maintenance records</li>
        <li><strong>Tyre Condition:</strong> Minimum 50% tread</li>
        <li><strong>Electrical:</strong> Lights, dashboard, sensors working</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Used Truck ROI: Real Example</h2>

      <h3>8-Year-Old Fuso Great (RM110,000)</h3>

      <p><strong>Investment:</strong> RM110,000 (0% down)</p>

      <p><strong>Monthly Net Profit:</strong>
  <br>• Revenue: RM80,000
  <br>• Operating costs: RM25,000
  <br>• Financing: RM2,000
  <br><strong>Net: RM53,000 per month</strong></p>

      <p><strong>Payback:</strong> 2 months</p>

      <p><strong>First Year Profit:</strong> RM636,000 - RM110,000 = RM526,000</p>

      <h2>Engine Life Reality</h2>

      <p><strong>Prime Mover Engine Life:</strong> 1-1.2 million km</p>

      <p><strong>8-Year-Old Truck with 600,000 km:</strong>
  <br>• 50-60% engine life remaining
  <br>• 5-7 more years of service
  <br>• Generates RM3-5 million revenue in remaining life</p>

      <h2>Risks and Mitigation</h2>

      <h3>Higher Maintenance</h3>

      <p><strong>Risk:</strong> Used trucks need RM2,500-RM3,500/month maintenance (vs RM2,000-RM2,500 new)</p>

      <p><strong>Mitigation:</strong> Build RM10,000 reserve before purchase</p>

      <h3>Unexpected Repairs</h3>

      <p><strong>Risk:</strong> Major repairs (engine, transmission) RM20,000-RM40,000</p>

      <p><strong>Mitigation:</strong> Keep RM20,000 emergency fund</p>

      <h2>When Used Makes Sense</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Limited startup capital</li>
        <li>Want to test transport business</li>
        <li>Need quick ROI</li>
        <li>Plan to upgrade later</li>
        <li>Experienced with truck maintenance</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Ing Heng Credit: Used Prime Mover Financing</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>0% down payment</li>
        <li>100% financing</li>
        <li>No age limit</li>
        <li>24-48 hour approval</li>
        <li>Assess condition, not age</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Success Story</h2>

      <p>"Bought 8-year-old Isuzu Giga for RM130,000 in 2024. 0% down payment. Bank rejected (too old). Ing Heng approved in 24 hours. Running Klang-Penang route. Monthly profit RM45,000-RM55,000. Truck paid off in 3 months. 18 months later, bought second used truck with profits. Both trucks generating RM100,000+ monthly profit. Used trucks let me start with RM0 down."</p>
      <p><em>— Muthu Kumaran, Transport Operator</em></p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Finance Used Prime Mover with 0% Down</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Any age, any condition. Approved in 24-48 hours.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Phone)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Get Used Prime Mover Financing" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 { color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  h3 { color: #8B6F47; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  p { line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  strong { color: #2D1810; font-weight: 700; }
  ul { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
  li { padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #D4A574; font-weight: bold; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  th { background: #2D1810; color: #F5F0E8; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; }
  td { border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; padding: 0.75rem; }
  em { display: block; margin-top: 0.5rem; color: #6B7280; font-style: normal; }
  br { display: none; }
</style>
